OL,3,CAll-women shortlist announced for
OL,4,Cdebut crime writer prize
OL,6,FShe said: "As a previous judge of the
OL,7,FWomen's Prize for Fiction, I am
OL,8,Fabsolutely delighted to see that the
OL,9,F2026 Bloody Scotland Debut shortlist
OL,10,Fis entirely made up of women.
OL,12,F"For decades, shortlists only had
OL,13,Foccasional women or none at all.
OL,15,F"A debut is always a howl into an
OL,16,Findifferent abyss. Sometimes the abyss
OL,17,Fis listening and it thinks you're
OL,18,Fbrilliant. Congratulations!"
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOUwD@AOUzD@\O]
