OL,3,CAll-women shortlist announced for
OL,4,Cdebut crime writer prize
OL,6,FThe judges for the prize are
OL,7,Fbroadcaster Bryan Burnett and crime
OL,8,Fwriter Vaseem Khan, and the judging
OL,9,Fpanel is chaired by Bloody Scotland co-
OL,10,Ffounder, Alex Gray.
OL,12,FShe said: "Lin Anderson and I decided
OL,13,Ffrom the start of Bloody Scotland that
OL,14,Fwe wanted to bring on the crime
OL,15,Fwriters of tomorrow as well as
OL,16,Fshowcasing the best of Scotland and
OL,17,Felsewhere.
OL,26,@tD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
