OL,3,CAll-women shortlist announced for
OL,4,Cdebut crime writer prize
OL,6,F"Now, as the chair of the judging
OL,7,Fpanel for the Bloody Scotland Debut
OL,8,FPrize, I'm thrilled to read the
OL,9,Fshortlist and help select the winner
OL,10,Feach year."
OL,12,FThe winner of the prize will be
OL,13,Fannounced on the opening night of the
OL,14,Ffestival at the Church of the Holy
OL,15,FRude on September 18.
OL,17,FThe prize is sponsored by The
OL,18,FGlencairn Glass.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]
