OL,3,CAll-women shortlist announced for
OL,4,Cdebut crime writer prize
OL,6,FKirsty Nicholson, marketing director
OL,7,Fat Glencairn, said: "We're always
OL,8,Fexcited to see the shortlist for the
OL,9,FBloody Scotland Debut Prize and this
OL,10,Fyear it's particularly encouraging to
OL,11,Fsee so many talented women represented.
OL,13,F"We're also delighted to see Frances
OL,14,FCrawford included following her
OL,15,Fsuccess in winning our 2023 Glencairn
OL,16,FGlass Crime Short Story Competition `
OL,17,Fit's wonderful to see her career
OL,18,Fcontinuing to flourish.
OL,26,@oD@UOUuD@AOU
